* databases - property that holds a List of Database instances 
* EXPORT_RC - request code used when exporting database
* exportIndex - used to identify which database to export after user chose location in export database dialog

* exportChosen(i) - called when user chose `export` option in database item menu
i - index of database that is to be exported
1. calls DatabaseFragment.showExportDialog(name)
name - name of the database retrieved from `databases` property by index `i`
2. saves database index `i` to exportIndex property

* exportDatabase(location) - exports database (identified by `exportIndex`):
1. retrieves location where to export database from given uri `location`
2. calls DatabasesModel.exportDatabase(name, location) in try-catch block
handling all errors:
2.1 if there are no errors - calls DatabaseFragment.showSuccessDialog(details) to
show dialog about success
details - details about successful operation
2.2 if there are any errors - calls DatabaseFragment.showErrorDialog(title, details)
to show error dialog with helpful information
title - title of error dialog
details - details about particular exception that occured
